title: Boeing strikes deal with Qatar Airways for purchase of 777X freighter jets
text:
The announcement was made at a White House event Monday with Stan Deal, the head of Boeing's commercial unit, Qatar Airways Chief Executive Officer Akbar Al Baker and U.S. Commerce Secretary Gina Raimondo.

An expanded version of this story appears on WSJ.com.
